  27 Jun 2012; Bernard Cafarelli <voyageur@gentoo.org> owncloud-3.0.3.ebuild,
  owncloud-4.0.2.ebuild:
  Enable sqlite3 by default (to have one backend enabled by default), bug
  #422821

*owncloud-4.0.2 (15 Jun 2012)

  15 Jun 2012; Bernard Cafarelli <voyageur@gentoo.org> -owncloud-4.0.0.ebuild,
  -owncloud-4.0.1.ebuild, +owncloud-4.0.2.ebuild:
  Version bump, mostly bugfixes and security updates. Removing previous 4.x
  versions

*owncloud-4.0.1 (07 Jun 2012)

  07 Jun 2012; Bernard Cafarelli <voyageur@gentoo.org> owncloud-4.0.0.ebuild,
  +owncloud-4.0.1.ebuild:
  Version bump, and depend on php with USE=pdo, bug #417599

